        <p>We're proud to share some big news: SonicHive has been honoured with the <strong>Superbrands 2025 Award for Workplace Innovation</strong>, recognising our acoustic pod solutions for their groundbreaking contribution to modern workplace design across the UAE. The win was first reported by <a href="https://www.khaleejtimes.com/kt-network/sonichive-wins-superbrands-2025-award" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--red);font-weight:500">Khaleej Times</a> on 6 November 2025, and it's a milestone we're thrilled to share with the team, our partners, and every client who has trusted us to rethink how their offices sound and feel.</p>

        <h2>The Award</h2>
        <p>Superbrands is one of the most respected independent brand authorities in the region, and its annual UAE awards recognise organisations that have made a measurable, lasting impact on their industry. For 2025, SonicHive was selected for the <strong>Workplace Innovation</strong> category — a recognition of how our acoustic pods have moved from a "nice-to-have" amenity to essential infrastructure for offices across Dubai and the wider Middle East.</p>

        <div class="award-card">
          <div class="award-row">
            <span class="award-label">Award</span>
            <span class="award-value">Superbrands 2025 — Workplace Innovation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="award-row">
            <span class="award-label">Recognised for</span>
            <span class="award-value">Groundbreaking contribution to modern workplace innovation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="award-row">
            <span class="award-label">Region</span>
            <span class="award-value">United Arab Emirates</span>
          </div>
          <div class="award-row">
            <span class="award-label">Reported</span>
            <span class="award-value">Khaleej Times, 6 November 2025</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>The Team Behind It</h2>
        <p>Awards like this are never won by a logo — they're won by the people who show up every day to design, build, and install the pods our clients rely on. SonicHive Directors <strong>Aneez Arakkal</strong> and <strong>Abbas Thirunavaya</strong> accepted the award alongside Operations Manager <strong>Bernadine Kamdin</strong> and <strong>Abdi Rahman Nooh</strong>, representing the wider SonicHive team across engineering, operations, and client delivery.</p>

        <blockquote><p>This recognition reflects our mission to elevate workplace wellness and productivity while shaping the future of adaptable, eco-conscious workspaces.</p></blockquote>

        <h2>What This Recognition Means</h2>
        <p>When we started SonicHive, the goal was simple: give teams a way to reclaim focus and privacy inside open-plan offices, without the cost and disruption of construction. Years later, that idea has scaled into a full range of acoustic pods — from compact VRT solo booths to modular VR meeting rooms and weatherproof outdoor pods — installed in offices, showrooms, and co-working spaces across the UAE.</p>
        <p>The Superbrands jury looks beyond product specs. They evaluate brand trust, market impact, and whether a company is genuinely changing how its industry operates. Being named a winner in the Workplace Innovation category tells us that the shift we set out to drive — from noisy, distracting offices to calm, adaptable workspaces — is being recognised at a regional level, not just by the clients who experience it pod by pod.</p>

        <h2>Where We Go From Here</h2>
        <p>This award doesn't change our roadmap — it confirms we're building the right thing. We'll keep investing in acoustic performance, sustainable materials, and faster installation, so that every new office, hotel, or villa in the UAE has a practical way to design for both wellness and productivity. If you haven't experienced a SonicHive pod yet, this is a good moment to start.</p>

        <p><a href="/about" style="color:var(--red);font-weight:500">Learn more about SonicHive →</a> or <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--red);font-weight:500">book a visit to our Dubai showroom →</a></p>

      </article>

